1
00:01:44,500 --> 00:01:47,500
[YUUKI] Long ago,
an all-powerful goddess

2
00:01:47,583 --> 00:01:49,791
created this world.

3
00:01:49,875 --> 00:01:55,083
Then, in order to create life,
she selflessly gave up her own.

4
00:01:55,166 --> 00:01:57,833
This is how we came to be.

5
00:01:57,916 --> 00:02:00,291
With her life force exhausted,

6
00:02:00,375 --> 00:02:04,166
the goddess began her eternal
slumber in an imperial tomb.

7
00:02:05,125 --> 00:02:08,375
Her death left behind a source
of unimaginable power.

8
00:02:12,208 --> 00:02:15,250
The goddess’s name was Bango.

9
00:02:15,333 --> 00:02:18,125
This is the myth of Creation

10
00:02:18,208 --> 00:02:22,291
that has been passed down
through the ages.

11
00:02:22,375 --> 00:02:24,416
[roaring]

12
00:02:24,500 --> 00:02:26,166
[rocks tumbling]

13
00:02:28,625 --> 00:02:31,375
-[SHIN, WEI shrieking]
-[SUIGIN yelling]

14
00:02:37,166 --> 00:02:38,458
[SHIN]
Excuse us!

15
00:02:38,541 --> 00:02:40,208
[WEI]
We’ll just hide in here, Star!

16
00:02:40,291 --> 00:02:42,750
[SHIN] We’re guides,
not fighters, Twin.

17
00:02:42,833 --> 00:02:44,125
[WEI]
We’ll leave the rest up to you.

18
00:02:44,208 --> 00:02:45,958
Go get ’em, Star!

19
00:02:46,041 --> 00:02:49,666
What can I do?
C’mon. Help me!

20
00:02:49,750 --> 00:02:51,208
I’m Shin, by the way.

21
00:02:51,291 --> 00:02:52,458
You can call me Wei!

22
00:02:52,541 --> 00:02:55,291
[BOTH]
Together, we are Twin Star!

23
00:02:55,375 --> 00:02:57,291
We’ll be right here,
cheering you on, Twin!

24
00:02:57,375 --> 00:02:59,250
We’ll be right here
cheering you on, Star!

25
00:02:59,333 --> 00:03:02,208
You’re running away?
What kind of guides are you?

26
00:03:02,291 --> 00:03:05,416
[YUUKI (DEMON LORD)]
You won't escape, little man!

27
00:03:07,250 --> 00:03:08,708
Would you stop
screaming everything?

28
00:03:08,791 --> 00:03:11,041
It’s obnoxious!
My ears work fine!

29
00:03:12,541 --> 00:03:13,750
Quite the attitude.

30
00:03:13,833 --> 00:03:15,833
You might be tougher
than I thought, boy.

31
00:03:15,916 --> 00:03:19,083
Very well!
Your worth will be tested!

32
00:03:19,166 --> 00:03:21,875
We’ll see if you can be
a Tomb Guardian.

33
00:03:21,958 --> 00:03:24,666
This stage has been
besieged by intruders.

34
00:03:24,750 --> 00:03:27,708
You will help me ward them off
and protect the treasures!

35
00:03:27,791 --> 00:03:29,583
That will be-- Huh?
Where'd he go?

36
00:03:29,666 --> 00:03:30,916
[grunts]

37
00:03:32,125 --> 00:03:33,541
[YUUKI (DEMON LORD)]
Hey! Wait!

38
00:03:33,625 --> 00:03:36,000
You disrespectful
little brat!

39
00:03:36,083 --> 00:03:38,583
Stop! I wasn’t done talking!

40
00:03:38,666 --> 00:03:41,583
[SUIGIN]
Yeah. That’s why I’m leaving.

41
00:03:41,666 --> 00:03:44,333
I guess you don’t want
to save Rei, then.

42
00:03:44,416 --> 00:03:46,416
How disappointing.

43
00:03:49,458 --> 00:03:51,416
If you don’t
pass the test, Suigin,

44
00:03:51,500 --> 00:03:53,833
saving Rei will be
forever out of your reach.

45
00:03:53,916 --> 00:03:55,208
What say you?

46
00:03:55,291 --> 00:03:57,666
How’d you know that?

47
00:03:59,791 --> 00:04:01,500
[energy rushing]

48
00:04:06,958 --> 00:04:08,125
[shattering]

49
00:04:08,208 --> 00:04:10,250
[explosions]

50
00:04:11,458 --> 00:04:14,416
[PHOEBE]
Aw, what a shame. You missed.

51
00:04:14,500 --> 00:04:15,541
Too far right.

52
00:04:15,625 --> 00:04:17,208
No freakin’ way.

53
00:04:17,291 --> 00:04:19,125
[PHOEBE]
Yes, freakin’ way.

54
00:04:19,208 --> 00:04:22,500
Don’t lose your cool, Eeyuu.
Next shot will do it.

55
00:04:22,583 --> 00:04:23,666
Try again.

56
00:04:23,750 --> 00:04:25,375
Roger that.

57
00:04:25,458 --> 00:04:27,875
Adjusting the firing angle.

58
00:04:27,958 --> 00:04:29,583
Lock and load.

59
00:04:29,666 --> 00:04:30,625
[chuckles]

60
00:04:30,708 --> 00:04:33,166
We're ready to rock, Phoebs.

61
00:04:33,250 --> 00:04:34,958
Five minutes
'til it’s recharged.

62
00:04:35,958 --> 00:04:37,666
[PHOEBE]
Far too long.

63
00:04:37,750 --> 00:04:41,041
Farin, be a dear and distract
it awhile, will you?

64
00:04:41,125 --> 00:04:42,166
Roger!

65
00:04:42,250 --> 00:04:43,875
[energy surging]

66
00:04:47,041 --> 00:04:48,000
[grunts]

67
00:04:48,083 --> 00:04:49,541
[energy rushing]

68
00:04:49,625 --> 00:04:50,958
[exploding]

69
00:04:55,500 --> 00:04:59,916
Great, just what I needed.
Hey. What’re you up to, Phoebe?

70
00:05:00,000 --> 00:05:03,416
Why, the usual, of course.
What else?

71
00:05:03,500 --> 00:05:04,583
Here we come.

72
00:05:06,083 --> 00:05:07,916
[SUIGIN]
Holy crap.

73
00:05:08,000 --> 00:05:09,333
That explosion.

74
00:05:09,416 --> 00:05:10,875
What happened?

75
00:05:10,958 --> 00:05:13,666
The tomb raiders attacked
sooner than expected.

76
00:05:13,750 --> 00:05:15,375
[SUIGIN]
Tomb raiders?

77
00:05:15,458 --> 00:05:18,750
As I was trying to say earlier,
you must fight them with me.

78
00:05:18,833 --> 00:05:21,791
That’s the only way to prove
you are worthy of the moniker.

79
00:05:21,875 --> 00:05:25,291
Enough!
Let’s get this over with.

80
00:05:25,375 --> 00:05:27,833
Much better.
That’s what I like to hear.

81
00:05:27,916 --> 00:05:30,541
Are you sure you’re prepared?

82
00:05:30,625 --> 00:05:31,916
[scoffs]

83
00:05:32,000 --> 00:05:33,958
Then let us begin!

84
00:05:34,041 --> 00:05:35,583
-[grunts]
-[energy surging]

85
00:05:41,083 --> 00:05:43,833
[SHOSTIA]
I am Shostia.

86
00:05:46,000 --> 00:05:48,958
The spirit of
the desert incarnate.

87
00:05:49,041 --> 00:05:50,791
[shimmering]

88
00:05:54,541 --> 00:05:56,125
[grunts]

89
00:05:56,208 --> 00:05:57,625
Excuse me, but...

90
00:05:57,708 --> 00:06:00,291
would you happen
to be young Master Suigin?

91
00:06:00,375 --> 00:06:03,625
Oh, uh...
yeah, that’s my name.

92
00:06:03,708 --> 00:06:04,916
Finally!

93
00:06:05,000 --> 00:06:06,875
I’ve been waiting for so long!

94
00:06:06,958 --> 00:06:09,500
I can’t believe
you’re really here!

95
00:06:14,708 --> 00:06:18,625
♪
[leaves rustling]

96
00:06:31,291 --> 00:06:33,250
It should all come
back to you now!

97
00:06:33,333 --> 00:06:35,583
The seal on your memories
is broken!

98
00:06:35,666 --> 00:06:38,416
I’m so happy for you
I could cry!

99
00:06:38,500 --> 00:06:42,291
I remember.
My grandpa.

100
00:06:42,375 --> 00:06:44,500
This scarf was from him.

101
00:06:44,583 --> 00:06:47,083
A gift from long ago.

102
00:06:55,958 --> 00:06:58,208
He really was...

103
00:06:58,291 --> 00:07:01,875
my grandfather.

104
00:07:01,958 --> 00:07:05,250
[YUUKI (DEMON LORD) chuckling]

105
00:07:05,333 --> 00:07:08,208
So, you finally remember,
Suigin, my boy?

106
00:07:08,291 --> 00:07:10,916
That voice. Just who are you?

107
00:07:11,000 --> 00:07:13,208
My Master!

108
00:07:13,291 --> 00:07:14,708
[evil chuckling]

109
00:07:16,916 --> 00:07:20,500
[YUUKI] Beloved grandson.
It’s been awhile.

110
00:07:20,583 --> 00:07:22,333
Lookin’ good, Suigin.

111
00:07:22,416 --> 00:07:23,666
[chuckles]

112
00:07:23,750 --> 00:07:24,916
What?

113
00:07:28,291 --> 00:07:30,791
[shimmering]

114
00:07:30,875 --> 00:07:33,291
[gasping, whimpering]

115
00:07:35,791 --> 00:07:38,250
[bubbling]

116
00:07:45,291 --> 00:07:46,875
[water rushing]

117
00:07:46,958 --> 00:07:49,166
[REI gasping]

118
00:07:52,541 --> 00:07:56,041
[KOSHIRIKO]
Look who decided to wake up.

119
00:07:56,125 --> 00:07:57,958
‘Bout time.

120
00:07:58,041 --> 00:07:59,625
Who are you?

121
00:08:01,333 --> 00:08:03,458
[KOSHIRIKO]
No time. Just put these on.

122
00:08:03,541 --> 00:08:05,833
Time for purification.

123
00:08:08,750 --> 00:08:11,458
Centipede Heart, let’s go!

124
00:08:11,541 --> 00:08:13,583
[air whooshing]

125
00:08:13,666 --> 00:08:15,583
[energy surging]

126
00:08:15,666 --> 00:08:17,791
[centipedes twittering]

127
00:08:17,875 --> 00:08:20,583
Alright now.
You know what to do, babies!

128
00:08:20,666 --> 00:08:23,625
Take care of those pesky
guardians!

129
00:08:25,291 --> 00:08:27,583
[SUIGIN]
You’re my gramps?

130
00:08:27,666 --> 00:08:30,375
But, aren’t you... ancient?

131
00:08:30,458 --> 00:08:31,666
And dead?

132
00:08:31,750 --> 00:08:33,916
I can understand
your confusion, my boy,

133
00:08:34,000 --> 00:08:36,000
so I’ll explain everything.

134
00:08:36,083 --> 00:08:38,666
At times, I was
the genius game designer.

135
00:08:38,750 --> 00:08:40,250
Others, I was the vice president

136
00:08:40,333 --> 00:08:42,208
of God Grave Tech company

137
00:08:42,291 --> 00:08:43,708
as well as the proud father

138
00:08:43,791 --> 00:08:46,083
who raised the beautiful
Rei Riku.

139
00:08:46,166 --> 00:08:49,333
But my true identity
has always been...

140
00:08:49,416 --> 00:08:51,000
[water gushing]

141
00:08:52,000 --> 00:08:55,250
Your grandfather,
the great Yuuki Riku!

142
00:08:55,333 --> 00:08:57,500
[exploding]

143
00:09:00,041 --> 00:09:01,125
[whimpering]

144
00:09:01,208 --> 00:09:03,083
[exploding continues]

145
00:09:03,166 --> 00:09:05,750
[yelling]

146
00:09:05,833 --> 00:09:07,458
♪

147
00:09:07,541 --> 00:09:09,166
[energy surging]

148
00:09:12,250 --> 00:09:14,500
One more time!

149
00:09:16,791 --> 00:09:19,000
Huh? Boo!

150
00:09:19,083 --> 00:09:21,041
And it was just starting
to get good!

151
00:09:22,500 --> 00:09:25,333
-[energy rushing]
-[centipedes twittering]

152
00:09:25,416 --> 00:09:28,041
Centipedes?
You’re Phoebe’s, right?

153
00:09:31,625 --> 00:09:33,500
Ah, yeah!

154
00:09:43,500 --> 00:09:45,666
Also, I’m sure you’re wondering
how I’m here,

155
00:09:45,750 --> 00:09:47,375
and it’s actually
quite simple.

156
00:09:47,458 --> 00:09:50,500
This is the data I saved of
myself just before I died.

157
00:09:50,583 --> 00:09:53,083
Now, do me a favor
and call me gramps again.

158
00:09:53,166 --> 00:09:56,458
I love it! Pretty please?

159
00:09:56,541 --> 00:09:58,458
This isn’t the time for that!

160
00:09:58,541 --> 00:10:01,333
Young Master!
We need to get inside!

161
00:10:01,416 --> 00:10:03,125
[SUIGIN yelling]

162
00:10:06,958 --> 00:10:08,791
[PHOEBE]
They’re really going at it.

163
00:10:08,875 --> 00:10:10,916
Let’s hurry up
and take care of this.

164
00:10:11,000 --> 00:10:13,958
That treasure is waiting
for us to find it.

165
00:10:14,041 --> 00:10:15,666
And get our hands on it.

166
00:10:15,750 --> 00:10:18,583
So we can make
our dreams come true!

167
00:10:19,583 --> 00:10:22,041
-[PHOEBE laughing]
-[EEYUU laughing]

168
00:10:24,833 --> 00:10:26,500
Where are we?

169
00:10:26,583 --> 00:10:29,041
The cockpit
of the Yuuki Thirty-Four.

170
00:10:29,125 --> 00:10:30,416
The Guardian Giant

171
00:10:30,500 --> 00:10:33,208
designed specifically for this
hidden level.

172
00:10:33,291 --> 00:10:34,541
[shimmering]

173
00:10:34,625 --> 00:10:35,833
[chuckles]

174
00:10:35,916 --> 00:10:37,750
Unbelievable!

175
00:10:37,833 --> 00:10:40,125
[explosions]

176
00:10:41,791 --> 00:10:43,250
Finally!

177
00:10:49,083 --> 00:10:52,166
[yelling]

178
00:10:52,250 --> 00:10:53,833
[exploding]

179
00:10:56,208 --> 00:10:58,000
[tomb cracking, thundering]

180
00:10:58,083 --> 00:10:59,750
I did it!

181
00:10:59,833 --> 00:11:01,791
The treasure’s ours!

182
00:11:08,000 --> 00:11:09,625
[explosions]

183
00:11:11,875 --> 00:11:13,916
What is that thing?

184
00:11:22,333 --> 00:11:24,916
[energy shimmers]

185
00:11:25,000 --> 00:11:26,958
[MERMAID 1] Gotta get you all
cleaned up!

186
00:11:27,041 --> 00:11:29,166
[MERMAID 2]
Come on, little miss sensitive!

187
00:11:29,250 --> 00:11:30,625
[mermaids giggling]

188
00:11:34,000 --> 00:11:35,041
[gasps]

189
00:11:35,125 --> 00:11:38,208
[MERMAID 2]
Are you having fun?

190
00:11:38,291 --> 00:11:40,083
Please! No more!

191
00:11:40,166 --> 00:11:42,708
[anguished cry]

192
00:13:15,416 --> 00:13:17,125
The Silver Guardian!

